title: Breakfast at Tiffany's
description:
Breakfast at Tiffany's, written by Caitlin Tegart. Stone Cold Fox at Maude Night, UCBTNY, April 14, 2008.

Starring Sean Clements, D'Arcy Erokan, Fran Gillespie, Nate Lang, Cody Melton & Joe Spellman. Directed by Dominic Dierkes.
